1
00:00:54,625 --> 00:00:57,917
YUMI'S CELLS 3

2
00:00:59,958 --> 00:01:02,917
EPISODE 19
EXPULSION ORDER

3
00:01:08,292 --> 00:01:09,334
Shin PD.

4
00:01:10,875 --> 00:01:12,958
I thought you went to see Mr. Kim.

5
00:01:13,875 --> 00:01:14,917
Why are you here?

6
00:01:15,250 --> 00:01:17,292
I felt like I had to see you first.

7
00:01:17,750 --> 00:01:18,791
Why?

8
00:01:21,083 --> 00:01:22,125
Why did you come here?

9
00:01:25,209 --> 00:01:26,209
Right.

10
00:01:26,292 --> 00:01:27,750
Why are you here, Soon-rok?

11
00:01:27,917 --> 00:01:29,292
Why did we come here?

12
00:01:29,750 --> 00:01:31,708
Why did Soon-rok come here?

13
00:01:34,375 --> 00:01:35,500
I don't know.

14
00:01:35,583 --> 00:01:37,042
What do you mean, you don't know?

15
00:01:38,458 --> 00:01:39,500
I don't know.

16
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,042
I'm not sure either...

17
00:01:42,250 --> 00:01:44,791
What? I don't know,
and you don't know either?

18
00:01:45,083 --> 00:01:47,083
What do you mean you don't know?

19
00:01:50,083 --> 00:01:52,500
Why did you break your plans
with Jennie and come here?

20
00:01:53,292 --> 00:01:55,791
- I don't know.
- You don't know that either?

21
00:01:58,375 --> 00:01:59,666
I shouldn't have done that.

22
00:02:00,416 --> 00:02:02,292
Get a grip, Soon-rok.

23
00:02:02,500 --> 00:02:04,042
What are you talking about?

24
00:02:04,458 --> 00:02:07,167
Why is Soon-rok acting like that
right now?

25
00:02:07,250 --> 00:02:09,374
I know. You shouldn't have.

26
00:02:11,042 --> 00:02:13,750
So, did you come here
to apologize to me for that?

27
00:02:16,334 --> 00:02:17,833
It's fine. I'm okay.

28
00:02:17,917 --> 00:02:20,292
- Just go to...
- I didn't come here to apologize.

29
00:02:24,958 --> 00:02:27,250
- Then why?
- I think...

30
00:02:32,541 --> 00:02:33,750
I like you.

31
00:02:59,833 --> 00:03:02,000
Emergency! Emergency!

32
00:03:03,416 --> 00:03:04,583
Everyone, it's an emergency!

33
00:03:04,666 --> 00:03:05,750
An emergency!

34
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:09,083
He likes Yu-mi?

35
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:11,125
Soon-rok confessed.

36
00:03:11,374 --> 00:03:13,374
Soon-rok likes Yu-mi?

37
00:03:14,125 --> 00:03:16,625
- Soon-rok likes Yu-mi.
- Soon-rok likes Yu-mi.

38
00:03:16,708 --> 00:03:18,917
- What? Since when?
- Since when?

39
00:03:19,167 --> 00:03:21,209
Soon-rok confessed!

40
00:03:33,583 --> 00:03:34,625
Wait.

41
00:03:36,875 --> 00:03:38,541
What is this...

42
00:03:38,625 --> 00:03:39,833
Is someone here?

43
00:03:41,125 --> 00:03:42,167
Shin PD!

44
00:03:43,209 --> 00:03:44,583
Are you okay?

45
00:03:45,708 --> 00:03:47,333
- Are you hurt?
- No.

46
00:03:47,583 --> 00:03:49,042
No, I'm fine.

47
00:03:50,083 --> 00:03:52,083
Na-hee was worried

48
00:03:52,167 --> 00:03:53,625
so she waited for you.

49
00:03:53,708 --> 00:03:54,791
Why did you do that?

50
00:03:54,875 --> 00:03:57,750
- I'm so curious.
- Well...

51
00:03:58,333 --> 00:04:00,250
I'm... sorry.

52
00:04:00,333 --> 00:04:02,000
Why did you two fight?

53
00:04:02,083 --> 00:04:03,875
We'll hear the details later.

54
00:04:03,958 --> 00:04:05,000
You should get going.

55
00:04:05,083 --> 00:04:06,250
The Chief Editor is waiting.

56
00:04:06,333 --> 00:04:07,917
Right, I'll be on my way.

57
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,083
But you just got here.

58
00:04:09,167 --> 00:04:10,333
Gosh, just hurry.

59
00:04:10,708 --> 00:04:11,750
Okay, then.

60
00:04:16,249 --> 00:04:18,167
By the way, why did he come here?

61
00:04:18,249 --> 00:04:19,791
I don't know.

62
00:04:20,291 --> 00:04:21,917
He was probably worried about us.

63
00:04:22,791 --> 00:04:24,750
Na-hee, you should go now.

64
00:04:24,833 --> 00:04:25,958
It's getting late.

65
00:04:26,249 --> 00:04:27,791
It's not that late yet.

66
00:04:28,291 --> 00:04:29,875
I'm leaving too, so let's go together.

67
00:04:29,958 --> 00:04:31,083
Hurry and get your things.

68
00:04:31,708 --> 00:04:32,708
But...

69
00:04:36,666 --> 00:04:38,000
Door closing.

70
00:04:48,042 --> 00:04:49,541
You're crazy.

71
00:04:50,791 --> 00:04:53,500
What is up with you today?

72
00:04:54,333 --> 00:04:55,458
Hey, what's wrong with him?

73
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:58,917
Why did Soon-rok
suddenly confess like that?

74
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,291
This is so absurd.

75
00:05:01,374 --> 00:05:03,541
Oh, about that.

76
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:06,083
Take a look at this.

77
00:05:10,249 --> 00:05:11,500
What's this?

78
00:05:11,791 --> 00:05:13,374
You performed the removal surgery.

79
00:05:13,541 --> 00:05:15,833
But it got bigger.

80
00:05:16,333 --> 00:05:17,333
No

81
00:05:17,416 --> 00:05:20,000
that's not an x-ray of Writer Yu-mi.

82
00:05:20,416 --> 00:05:21,750
It's Soon-rok's.

83
00:05:22,583 --> 00:05:23,583
What?

84
00:05:23,666 --> 00:05:25,875
It was only this big earlier.

85
00:05:26,125 --> 00:05:27,708
But I took an x-ray today

86
00:05:28,083 --> 00:05:29,374
and it's gotten this big.

87
00:05:30,833 --> 00:05:33,875
Then why did he even draw the line?

88
00:05:36,208 --> 00:05:37,208
I...

89
00:05:38,042 --> 00:05:39,500
made a misdiagnosis.

90
00:05:40,458 --> 00:05:41,500
I'm sorry.

91
00:05:41,917 --> 00:05:44,000
Everything's a mess because of me.

92
00:05:44,791 --> 00:05:47,125
Do you think "sorry" is going to fix this?

93
00:05:49,291 --> 00:05:51,374
You quack...

94
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:53,083
A quack...

95
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:54,708
Hey, where are you going?

96
00:05:55,791 --> 00:05:57,166
I'll fix it.

97
00:05:57,249 --> 00:05:58,249
Just wait.

98
00:05:59,166 --> 00:06:01,333
What are you going to fix?

99
00:06:06,583 --> 00:06:08,125
- Someone's coming!
- Who is it?

100
00:06:11,125 --> 00:06:12,666
Hey, guys!

101
00:06:17,333 --> 00:06:19,791
I'm Soon-rok's Love Cell.

102
00:06:20,708 --> 00:06:21,958
Love Cell?

103
00:06:22,458 --> 00:06:23,833
Can you open the door?

104
00:06:25,042 --> 00:06:27,166
I have something to say

105
00:06:27,458 --> 00:06:28,583
to Yu-mi's Love Cell.

106
00:06:30,833 --> 00:06:32,416
Soon-rok's Love Cell?

107
00:06:32,583 --> 00:06:33,875
Yeah, what should we do?

108
00:06:33,958 --> 00:06:35,000
Should we let him in?

109
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,666
Wow, he came all this way?

110
00:06:38,083 --> 00:06:39,708
This is for real.

111
00:06:40,249 --> 00:06:42,249
It was a real confession.

112
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:44,917
What's gotten into him?

113
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,500
There's one more thing that's changed

114
00:06:58,583 --> 00:06:59,958
as I've gotten older.

115
00:07:01,042 --> 00:07:02,291
Open the door.

116
00:07:04,833 --> 00:07:06,124
Let's call Love!

117
00:07:06,208 --> 00:07:07,208
Hold on.

118
00:07:07,291 --> 00:07:08,666
You stay put.

119
00:07:08,791 --> 00:07:10,208
Let go of me!

120
00:07:10,291 --> 00:07:12,958
I, Rational Cell, can feel
my power getting stronger too.

121
00:07:14,917 --> 00:07:15,917
Thanks.

122
00:07:17,042 --> 00:07:18,042
Get him!

123
00:07:21,958 --> 00:07:23,416
What's wrong with you?

124
00:07:26,124 --> 00:07:27,208
Now...

125
00:07:27,458 --> 00:07:28,917
the trial will begin.

126
00:07:30,291 --> 00:07:31,625
The charges against the defendant
Shin Soon-rok

127
00:07:31,708 --> 00:07:32,750
are as follows.

128
00:07:33,708 --> 00:07:35,333
First, Shin Soon-rok

129
00:07:35,416 --> 00:07:37,625
acted bizarrely from day one

130
00:07:37,708 --> 00:07:39,583
confusing Yu-mi

131
00:07:39,666 --> 00:07:42,917
and often disrupting her writing.
Do you accept this?

132
00:07:43,082 --> 00:07:44,500
Let's talk, Shin PD.

133
00:07:44,833 --> 00:07:46,458
Are you unhappy working with me?

134
00:07:46,666 --> 00:07:48,166
- Yes, yes, I understand.
- Huh? Excuse me.

135
00:07:48,249 --> 00:07:49,374
- Bye.
- Hello?

136
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:51,541
Hey!

137
00:07:52,666 --> 00:07:53,666
Ms. Kim.

138
00:07:53,833 --> 00:07:54,833
Ms. Kim.

139
00:07:59,416 --> 00:08:00,708
Well...

140
00:08:00,791 --> 00:08:02,124
It wasn't intentional...

141
00:08:02,875 --> 00:08:03,958
DEFENDANT

142
00:08:04,041 --> 00:08:05,166
I'm sorry

143
00:08:06,333 --> 00:08:07,333
if I made you uncomfortable.

144
00:08:07,416 --> 00:08:08,541
Do you admit it?

145
00:08:09,583 --> 00:08:11,333
I admit it.

146
00:08:12,208 --> 00:08:13,249
Second.

147
00:08:14,875 --> 00:08:17,458
The crime of making
her heart flutter with his cute smile

148
00:08:17,541 --> 00:08:18,875
and puppy charm.

149
00:08:23,917 --> 00:08:25,458
- He was just like a puppy.
- He was cute.

150
00:08:25,541 --> 00:08:27,666
He is cute. I really remember that.

151
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:29,082
He was cute.

152
00:08:29,583 --> 00:08:30,708
Do you admit it?

153
00:08:31,291 --> 00:08:32,750
That's just

154
00:08:32,833 --> 00:08:35,082
- Soon-rok's charm...
-Do you admit it?

155
00:08:36,208 --> 00:08:37,583
I admit it.

156
00:08:37,666 --> 00:08:38,666
Third.

157
00:08:38,875 --> 00:08:40,458
Texting her to see a movie.

158
00:08:40,791 --> 00:08:41,791
You're cool.

159
00:08:41,875 --> 00:08:43,333
Spouting the word "cool" carelessly

160
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:46,291
and sharing his umbrella in the rain

161
00:08:46,374 --> 00:08:48,750
making Yu-mi's heart flutter.

162
00:08:51,958 --> 00:08:53,999
My heart really fluttered that day.

163
00:08:55,249 --> 00:08:56,291
Do you admit it?

164
00:08:58,500 --> 00:08:59,708
I admit it.

165
00:09:00,291 --> 00:09:01,291
Fourth.

166
00:09:01,541 --> 00:09:02,708
The crime of leading her on

167
00:09:02,791 --> 00:09:05,333
then asking her to get him a blind date
and confusing her.

168
00:09:07,208 --> 00:09:09,458
Someone for a blind date.

169
00:09:11,957 --> 00:09:13,082
That's right.

170
00:09:13,166 --> 00:09:14,791
I was so pissed off then.

171
00:09:14,875 --> 00:09:15,875
Seriously.

172
00:09:16,249 --> 00:09:17,291
Do you admit it?

173
00:09:18,416 --> 00:09:19,416
I admit it.

174
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:20,500
- Fifth.
- There's more?

175
00:09:21,041 --> 00:09:23,416
After going on a date with Yu-mi's junior

176
00:09:23,708 --> 00:09:26,082
you canceled last minute, hurting Jennie

177
00:09:26,374 --> 00:09:28,333
and making it awkward for the matchmaker.

178
00:09:28,666 --> 00:09:29,666
Do you admit it?

179
00:09:29,957 --> 00:09:31,082
I admit it.

180
00:09:31,166 --> 00:09:32,917
That was truly wrong.

181
00:09:33,166 --> 00:09:34,625
But this happened

182
00:09:34,708 --> 00:09:37,999
because Soon-rok
hadn't realized his feelings yet...

183
00:09:38,082 --> 00:09:39,082
Sixth.

184
00:09:39,166 --> 00:09:41,791
For suddenly confessing his feelings now

185
00:09:41,875 --> 00:09:44,458
and making all their relationships
a complete mess.

186
00:09:44,541 --> 00:09:45,583
Do you admit it?

187
00:09:47,166 --> 00:09:48,166
Admit it.

188
00:09:48,249 --> 00:09:50,291
- You have to admit it.
- Admit it!

189
00:09:50,374 --> 00:09:51,583
- Come on!
- Do it!

190
00:09:53,291 --> 00:09:54,291
I admit it.

191
00:09:54,875 --> 00:09:56,833
The defendant has admitted to all charges.

192
00:09:57,166 --> 00:09:58,416
Defendant Shin Soon-rok

193
00:09:58,500 --> 00:09:59,999
caused a stir in Yu-mi Village

194
00:10:00,291 --> 00:10:02,124
delaying her work.

195
00:10:02,208 --> 00:10:05,625
And is found guilty of dealing
a fatal blow to her relationships.

196
00:10:06,166 --> 00:10:07,333
Therefore...

197
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,750
the verdict.

198
00:10:09,291 --> 00:10:10,916
Shin Soon-rok's confession...

199
00:10:13,458 --> 00:10:14,750
is rejected.

200
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:18,916
- Reject his confession?
- Emotional, sit down.

201
00:10:20,750 --> 00:10:24,291
At the same time, to prevent
Shin Soon-rok's further influence

202
00:10:24,666 --> 00:10:26,625
I order his banishment from Yu-mi Village.

203
00:10:28,166 --> 00:10:29,166
Soon-rok is

204
00:10:29,249 --> 00:10:31,957
out of Yu-mi's Village!

205
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:43,833
Are you okay?

206
00:10:45,291 --> 00:10:46,666
Get out of here now!

207
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:47,750
Get out!

208
00:11:28,124 --> 00:11:29,166
Shin PD.

209
00:11:30,082 --> 00:11:31,333
I'll pretend I didn't hear

210
00:11:31,416 --> 00:11:32,832
what you just said.

211
00:11:33,666 --> 00:11:35,625
I didn't know you were this immature.

212
00:11:36,500 --> 00:11:37,750
You're being very reckless.

213
00:11:39,666 --> 00:11:41,625
Apologize to Writer Ju-ho

214
00:11:42,041 --> 00:11:43,999
and I hope you sort this out.

215
00:12:30,583 --> 00:12:32,333
Smells nice.

216
00:12:43,790 --> 00:12:44,832
It's delicious.

217
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:54,957
My mind feels calm
for the first time in a while.

218
00:12:55,458 --> 00:12:57,082
This is the real Yu-mi.

219
00:13:01,832 --> 00:13:04,416
My mornings always used to
start like this.

220
00:13:04,625 --> 00:13:07,458
Calmly thinking about
what to write for the day.

221
00:13:09,374 --> 00:13:11,166
It's finally peaceful.

222
00:13:14,707 --> 00:13:15,874
Soon-rok.

223
00:13:16,999 --> 00:13:19,374
Soon-rok. It's already 11 o'clock.

224
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:21,583
I know.

225
00:13:21,666 --> 00:13:24,333
How long are you going to
lie here like this?

226
00:13:26,707 --> 00:13:27,707
I have no energy.

227
00:13:28,541 --> 00:13:29,541
I can't get up.

228
00:13:37,208 --> 00:13:38,625
Oh, no.

229
00:13:39,249 --> 00:13:42,208
Even though I've been lying at home
all day, it's not recharging.

230
00:13:42,625 --> 00:13:43,790
What should I do?

231
00:13:46,041 --> 00:13:49,041
But there's one thing
left to do, Soon-rok.

232
00:13:49,666 --> 00:13:51,832
You have to contact Jennie.

233
00:13:56,166 --> 00:13:58,124
Use your last bit of strength.

234
00:13:58,458 --> 00:14:01,583
Let's finish this with some manners.

235
00:14:23,625 --> 00:14:24,625
Jennie.

236
00:14:25,166 --> 00:14:27,790
I'm so sorry about yesterday.

237
00:14:33,291 --> 00:14:34,416
The truth is

238
00:14:34,500 --> 00:14:36,583
I haven't had much time lately...

239
00:14:38,291 --> 00:14:39,291
It's Jennie.

240
00:14:44,416 --> 00:14:45,416
Hello?

241
00:14:46,916 --> 00:14:47,916
Yes, Jennie.

242
00:14:48,124 --> 00:14:49,999
Soon-rok, are you busy?

243
00:14:50,416 --> 00:14:51,832
Is it okay to talk for a moment?

244
00:14:52,957 --> 00:14:53,957
Yes.

245
00:14:54,208 --> 00:14:56,500
I'm really sorry about yesterday.

246
00:15:06,749 --> 00:15:08,624
JENNIE

247
00:15:10,249 --> 00:15:11,541
Hey, Jennie.

248
00:15:12,208 --> 00:15:13,707
I meant to call you yesterday

249
00:15:13,790 --> 00:15:15,707
but it got too late.

250
00:15:16,665 --> 00:15:18,208
You were baffled yesterday, right?

251
00:15:18,999 --> 00:15:19,999
Yes.

252
00:15:20,124 --> 00:15:21,333
I was a bit baffled.

253
00:15:22,166 --> 00:15:23,916
It seems he had something urgent

254
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:26,874
at the publishing company.

255
00:15:27,124 --> 00:15:29,249
I couldn't ask for details either.

256
00:15:29,916 --> 00:15:32,957
But I'll ask Shin PD during our meeting.

257
00:15:33,874 --> 00:15:35,458
I already spoke with Soon-rok.

258
00:15:35,790 --> 00:15:36,790
A little while ago.

259
00:15:36,874 --> 00:15:37,916
Oh, really?

260
00:15:38,416 --> 00:15:39,790
He seemed really sorry.

261
00:15:40,291 --> 00:15:41,541
He asked to meet today.

262
00:15:41,665 --> 00:15:43,082
So you agreed to meet?

263
00:15:43,374 --> 00:15:44,374
No.

264
00:15:44,624 --> 00:15:45,624
Yu-mi.

265
00:15:46,041 --> 00:15:47,082
Actually...

266
00:15:49,707 --> 00:15:51,082
Jeong-sik suddenly

267
00:15:52,166 --> 00:15:53,500
contacted me.

268
00:15:54,874 --> 00:15:57,582
Your ex-boyfriend?

269
00:15:58,333 --> 00:15:59,333
Yes.

270
00:15:59,749 --> 00:16:02,166
It's been a little over two months
since we broke up.

271
00:16:02,665 --> 00:16:04,416
But he suddenly came over last night

272
00:16:06,082 --> 00:16:07,707
so we decided

273
00:16:08,624 --> 00:16:10,333
to get back together.

274
00:16:11,124 --> 00:16:12,124
Oh.

275
00:16:13,374 --> 00:16:14,374
I see.

276
00:16:14,458 --> 00:16:15,624
I'm so sorry.

277
00:16:16,124 --> 00:16:17,291
This all happened so suddenly.

278
00:16:17,749 --> 00:16:18,790
No, it's okay.

279
00:16:19,916 --> 00:16:22,333
It's... a good thing.

280
00:16:23,124 --> 00:16:24,540
That's great.

281
00:16:24,624 --> 00:16:28,124
I felt I should tell you the truth.

282
00:16:30,582 --> 00:16:32,500
Yu-mi didn't know when she set us up.

283
00:16:32,582 --> 00:16:33,665
Please don't misunderstand.

284
00:16:33,790 --> 00:16:34,832
Yes.

285
00:16:35,166 --> 00:16:36,249
Of course.

286
00:16:36,582 --> 00:16:38,999
I'll tell Yu-mi too.

287
00:16:39,374 --> 00:16:40,374
Okay.

288
00:16:42,291 --> 00:16:43,291
I'm sorry.

289
00:16:43,374 --> 00:16:45,540
No, don't worry about it.

290
00:16:46,041 --> 00:16:47,208
Congratulations.

291
00:16:47,499 --> 00:16:48,790
It feels a bit strange for me

292
00:16:48,874 --> 00:16:50,166
to say thank you...

293
00:16:50,582 --> 00:16:51,749
I'm truly happy for you.

294
00:16:53,082 --> 00:16:54,124
I mean it.

295
00:17:01,291 --> 00:17:03,540
I told Soon-rok

296
00:17:04,249 --> 00:17:05,374
and I feel so bad.

297
00:17:05,957 --> 00:17:06,957
Well...

298
00:17:08,291 --> 00:17:10,041
I'm sure he'll understand.

299
00:17:10,208 --> 00:17:11,916
I'm so sorry to you too, Yu-mi.

300
00:17:11,999 --> 00:17:13,208
Gosh, it's fine.

301
00:17:14,874 --> 00:17:15,874
That's great.

302
00:17:16,458 --> 00:17:17,458
Really great.

303
00:17:22,082 --> 00:17:23,082
Yu-mi.

304
00:17:23,166 --> 00:17:24,582
Call me when you're done
with your deadline.

305
00:17:24,749 --> 00:17:26,082
I'll buy you a meal.

306
00:17:26,291 --> 00:17:27,457
Thank you, Yu-mi.

307
00:17:28,082 --> 00:17:29,874
Okay, sure. See you later.

308
00:17:38,166 --> 00:17:39,416
What the heck?

309
00:17:40,374 --> 00:17:42,665
If she was getting back with him,
she should've done it a day earlier.

310
00:17:43,124 --> 00:17:45,041
We wouldn't have kicked him out.

311
00:17:46,582 --> 00:17:48,999
Can't we go see Soon-rok?

312
00:17:50,707 --> 00:17:51,999
It's over now.

313
00:17:52,082 --> 00:17:53,082
How so?

314
00:17:53,166 --> 00:17:54,916
Soon-rok said he likes Yu-mi

315
00:17:55,041 --> 00:17:56,665
and Yu-mi liked Soon-rok too.

316
00:17:56,790 --> 00:17:58,124
We already wrapped it up

317
00:17:58,333 --> 00:17:59,457
neatly.

318
00:18:00,124 --> 00:18:01,457
That's right.

319
00:18:02,291 --> 00:18:03,749
- What's done is done.
- It's over.

320
00:18:05,415 --> 00:18:07,041
What's done is done.

321
00:18:07,333 --> 00:18:08,457
It's deceitful

322
00:18:08,540 --> 00:18:10,957
- to break our word.
- That's not good manners.

323
00:18:11,041 --> 00:18:12,790
Let's not do that.

324
00:18:12,874 --> 00:18:15,415
You've got to be kidding me.

325
00:18:17,082 --> 00:18:18,374
Where is she going?

326
00:18:27,582 --> 00:18:28,749
You cold-hearted things.

327
00:18:29,166 --> 00:18:30,999
That's how a person's heart is.

328
00:18:31,082 --> 00:18:32,415
Doesn't it change
depending on the situation?

329
00:18:32,624 --> 00:18:33,624
Fine.

330
00:18:33,707 --> 00:18:35,374
If you all don't want to,
I'll do it myself.

331
00:18:37,707 --> 00:18:39,415
Let's go, Yu-mi.

332
00:18:43,041 --> 00:18:45,916
We're going to Soon-rok.

333
00:18:46,291 --> 00:18:47,415
Starting now

334
00:18:48,249 --> 00:18:51,540
it's Heart Fever Time!

335
00:18:51,624 --> 00:18:52,790
HEART FEVER TIME
WHEN EMOTIONS EXPLODE

336
00:18:52,874 --> 00:18:54,124
Heart Fever Time.

337
00:18:54,208 --> 00:18:56,499
A state where emotions
temporarily explode.

338
00:18:56,749 --> 00:18:59,249
When in this state,
there's nothing you can't do.

339
00:19:03,333 --> 00:19:05,208
Heart Fever Time!

340
00:19:05,874 --> 00:19:06,874
Time!

341
00:19:06,957 --> 00:19:08,749
Time, time!

342
00:19:08,832 --> 00:19:11,874
- Time!
- Emotional.

343
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:14,082
Enough.

344
00:19:16,665 --> 00:19:17,707
Move.

345
00:19:17,790 --> 00:19:18,874
I'm good at this.

346
00:19:19,333 --> 00:19:21,166
Don't you remember
what happened with Ba-bi?

347
00:19:21,249 --> 00:19:22,624
Heart Fever Time.

348
00:19:22,874 --> 00:19:23,874
Don't you know

349
00:19:23,957 --> 00:19:25,249
that has an age limit?

350
00:19:26,540 --> 00:19:28,166
-Yu-mi can't do that anymore.

351
00:19:30,082 --> 00:19:31,499
Sadly, Heart Fever Time

352
00:19:31,582 --> 00:19:33,499
has an age limit.

353
00:19:34,373 --> 00:19:35,999
The ability disappears

354
00:19:36,457 --> 00:19:38,208
in your mid-thirties.

355
00:19:53,457 --> 00:19:54,707
However

356
00:19:54,790 --> 00:19:56,166
Heart Fever Time

357
00:19:56,249 --> 00:19:58,124
isn't an ability only Yu-mi can use.

358
00:20:03,957 --> 00:20:06,291
Heart Fever Time will now begin.

359
00:20:10,540 --> 00:20:11,665
What's going on?

360
00:20:15,790 --> 00:20:17,582
It's Emotional's house!

361
00:20:23,874 --> 00:20:26,373
This is Heart Fever Time.

362
00:20:26,457 --> 00:20:27,999
Heart Fever Time?

363
00:20:28,082 --> 00:20:29,082
Really?

364
00:20:29,499 --> 00:20:31,124
I've only heard about it.

365
00:20:31,582 --> 00:20:33,290
This is the first time
I've seen it in our village.

366
00:20:35,373 --> 00:20:37,332
EMOTIONAL CELL

367
00:20:39,249 --> 00:20:40,874
Soon-rok, let's go!

368
00:20:40,957 --> 00:20:42,499
We're going to Ms. Kim, no...

369
00:20:43,124 --> 00:20:45,790
We're going to Yu-mi!

370
00:21:13,874 --> 00:21:15,624
Run, Soon-rok!

371
00:22:04,874 --> 00:22:06,207
I guess she's not home.

372
00:22:07,373 --> 00:22:08,790
This was a bad idea.

373
00:22:08,874 --> 00:22:10,457
She clearly rejected you.

374
00:22:10,540 --> 00:22:12,499
What did you expect to hear?

375
00:22:15,957 --> 00:22:17,207
Think about it.

376
00:22:17,290 --> 00:22:18,707
The age difference is huge.

377
00:22:18,790 --> 00:22:20,874
She won't even see you as a man.

378
00:22:36,749 --> 00:22:38,082
Let's go back.

379
00:22:38,165 --> 00:22:40,332
This isn't like you.

380
00:23:06,248 --> 00:23:07,332
Soon-rok.

381
00:23:07,665 --> 00:23:10,207
Thank you for understanding
and for your support.

382
00:23:10,290 --> 00:23:11,499
Take care.

383
00:23:11,582 --> 00:23:13,499
Someday we'll see each other again, right?

384
00:23:17,790 --> 00:23:18,790
Yes.

385
00:23:18,874 --> 00:23:20,582
You take care too, Jennie.

386
00:23:27,457 --> 00:23:29,499
Maybe we'll see each other
at Yu-mi's wedding?

387
00:23:30,665 --> 00:23:31,790
Though there's no set date.

388
00:23:34,082 --> 00:23:35,832
A wedding?

389
00:23:39,415 --> 00:23:41,290
Hurry up and come.

390
00:23:42,499 --> 00:23:43,540
I think we...

391
00:23:44,457 --> 00:23:46,081
You look so pretty.

392
00:23:47,790 --> 00:23:49,290
Shin PD, come over here.

393
00:23:49,373 --> 00:23:50,957
Oh, my.

394
00:23:51,707 --> 00:23:52,916
Come on up.

395
00:23:54,707 --> 00:23:56,165
Thank you.

396
00:24:04,290 --> 00:24:06,165
He's the editor in charge.

397
00:24:09,123 --> 00:24:10,207
Soon-rok.

398
00:24:10,540 --> 00:24:11,707
Hello.

399
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:12,790
It's been a while.

400
00:24:17,874 --> 00:24:18,999
Come on up.

401
00:24:19,290 --> 00:24:20,916
No, no.

402
00:24:21,457 --> 00:24:23,248
I don't want to imagine that.

403
00:24:24,582 --> 00:24:27,415
So squeeze it out one more time!

404
00:24:27,749 --> 00:24:30,165
It's Heart Fever Time!

405
00:24:57,916 --> 00:24:59,707
Run, Soon-rok!

406
00:25:05,624 --> 00:25:09,998
ONE WAY

407
00:25:19,081 --> 00:25:20,123
Hello.

408
00:26:03,998 --> 00:26:05,207
Who is it?

409
00:26:05,916 --> 00:26:06,956
Ms. Kim.

410
00:26:07,248 --> 00:26:08,373
It's me, Soon-rok.

411
00:26:10,415 --> 00:26:11,457
But haven't I seen

412
00:26:11,707 --> 00:26:13,624
this scene somewhere before?

413
00:26:19,624 --> 00:26:20,624
Shin PD?

414
00:26:21,207 --> 00:26:22,207
That's right.

415
00:26:22,290 --> 00:26:24,582
This is the exact same situation
as yesterday.

416
00:26:26,540 --> 00:26:27,624
What are you doing here?

417
00:26:28,540 --> 00:26:31,832
It's the same as yesterday. Damn it.

418
00:26:33,248 --> 00:26:34,290
Why did you come...

419
00:26:35,415 --> 00:26:36,998
without calling?

420
00:26:43,499 --> 00:26:44,499
Huh?

421
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:50,790
Don't tell me...

422
00:26:51,665 --> 00:26:53,332
You don't know again?

423
00:26:54,040 --> 00:26:55,749
- What on earth...
- No.

424
00:27:01,457 --> 00:27:03,248
Everything you said is right, Ms. Kim.

425
00:27:04,457 --> 00:27:06,790
I'm very immature.

426
00:27:08,790 --> 00:27:09,956
And I was reckless.

427
00:27:12,248 --> 00:27:13,248
I admit it.

428
00:27:15,873 --> 00:27:16,998
It's ridiculous.

429
00:27:18,373 --> 00:27:19,373
So sudden

430
00:27:19,873 --> 00:27:20,956
and out of the blue.

431
00:27:25,373 --> 00:27:26,373
But...

432
00:27:27,749 --> 00:27:28,749
But still...

433
00:27:35,540 --> 00:27:37,248
No matter how much I think about it...

434
00:27:40,415 --> 00:27:41,540
I like you, Ms. Kim.

435
00:27:43,749 --> 00:27:45,749
It's pathetic that
I've only just realized it...

436
00:27:48,248 --> 00:27:49,665
I think I've liked you...

437
00:27:52,248 --> 00:27:53,831
from the beginning.

438
00:28:16,915 --> 00:28:17,915
Yesterday...

439
00:28:20,415 --> 00:28:21,582
you told me.

440
00:28:24,790 --> 00:28:25,790
Yes.

441
00:28:26,540 --> 00:28:27,665
And...

442
00:28:28,956 --> 00:28:30,457
I rejected you.

443
00:28:32,332 --> 00:28:33,373
Yes.

444
00:28:33,457 --> 00:28:34,831
But you're saying the same thing...

445
00:28:37,457 --> 00:28:38,457
again.

446
00:28:41,831 --> 00:28:42,831
Yes.

447
00:28:49,789 --> 00:28:51,165
Because I think I'll regret it.

448
00:28:59,789 --> 00:29:00,956
There's no answer.

449
00:29:02,165 --> 00:29:04,081
Did I get rejected again?

450
00:29:05,915 --> 00:29:07,207
Let's go.

451
00:29:08,165 --> 00:29:10,081
Soon-rok got rejected twice in a row.

452
00:29:10,457 --> 00:29:12,540
I've never experienced such humiliation.

453
00:29:21,915 --> 00:29:22,956
But...

454
00:29:24,415 --> 00:29:25,956
Have you had lunch?

455
00:29:29,457 --> 00:29:30,499
No.

456
00:29:31,499 --> 00:29:33,831
Do you want to eat together?

457
00:29:51,165 --> 00:29:52,540
It opened!

458
00:29:57,457 --> 00:29:58,748
It opened!

459
00:30:11,165 --> 00:30:12,165
He's here again.

460
00:30:12,789 --> 00:30:14,748
He got kicked out, but he's back.

461
00:30:14,831 --> 00:30:16,040
How brave.

462
00:30:16,123 --> 00:30:18,540
What if he gets kicked out again?

463
00:30:18,624 --> 00:30:19,831
Hang in there.

464
00:30:21,081 --> 00:30:22,415
- Welcome!
- Cheer up, Soon-rok!

465
00:30:22,706 --> 00:30:24,956
- Welcome, Shin Soon-rok!
- You can do it!

466
00:30:25,415 --> 00:30:26,457
Thanks.

467
00:30:27,956 --> 00:30:31,165
I came to see Yu-mi's Love Cell.

468
00:30:31,665 --> 00:30:34,290
If you want to see Love, go that way.

469
00:30:34,373 --> 00:30:36,499
- Okay.
- I'll be cheering for you.

470
00:30:36,582 --> 00:30:38,123
- Be careful!
- Thanks!

471
00:30:55,540 --> 00:30:56,624
Hello.

472
00:30:57,457 --> 00:30:58,956
You must be Love.

473
00:30:59,290 --> 00:31:01,332
Ms. Kim is on another level.

474
00:31:01,582 --> 00:31:03,873
Having such a huge Love is why

475
00:31:03,956 --> 00:31:06,123
she's a master of romance stories.

476
00:31:06,956 --> 00:31:09,373
I'm not Love. I'm Hunger.

477
00:31:10,415 --> 00:31:11,998
Love lives over there.

478
00:31:12,081 --> 00:31:13,081
Go over there.

479
00:31:13,165 --> 00:31:14,831
Is that so?

480
00:31:15,248 --> 00:31:16,290
Thanks.

481
00:31:18,040 --> 00:31:19,040
Wait!

482
00:31:19,123 --> 00:31:21,332
But have you had lunch?

483
00:31:21,582 --> 00:31:22,706
Lunch?

484
00:31:22,956 --> 00:31:26,081
Love is great, but you have to eat.

485
00:31:28,373 --> 00:31:29,582
Have you had lunch?

486
00:31:31,457 --> 00:31:32,998
- No.
- Do you want to

487
00:31:33,499 --> 00:31:34,499
eat together?

488
00:31:36,706 --> 00:31:37,706
Come in.

489
00:31:52,831 --> 00:31:55,415
I was just about to have lunch.

490
00:31:58,081 --> 00:32:00,081
Do you like naengmyeon?

491
00:32:01,623 --> 00:32:02,956
I'm going to make bibim-naengmyeon.

492
00:32:06,165 --> 00:32:07,499
- So?
- What?

493
00:32:08,457 --> 00:32:09,581
Is bibim-naengmyeon...

494
00:32:10,081 --> 00:32:11,081
okay?

495
00:32:12,915 --> 00:32:14,165
Yes, yes.

496
00:32:14,956 --> 00:32:15,956
That's great.

497
00:32:20,499 --> 00:32:21,499
Have a seat.

498
00:32:44,581 --> 00:32:45,623
Hi.

499
00:32:45,748 --> 00:32:47,373
Is Love Cell's house around here?

500
00:32:47,706 --> 00:32:49,623
Are you Soon-rok's Love Cell?

501
00:32:49,915 --> 00:32:51,457
Yeah. It's nice to meet you.

502
00:32:51,539 --> 00:32:52,956
I'll be coming here often.

503
00:32:53,207 --> 00:32:54,831
- You'll be coming here often?
- Yeah.

504
00:32:55,123 --> 00:32:56,539
Weren't you banished?

505
00:32:56,789 --> 00:32:58,290
Do you have the right to be here?

506
00:33:00,915 --> 00:33:02,956
You can eat two servings, right?

507
00:33:03,581 --> 00:33:04,998
Then I'll have to make four.

508
00:33:05,956 --> 00:33:06,956
Four?

509
00:33:09,332 --> 00:33:10,789
Because there are three of us.

510
00:33:11,623 --> 00:33:13,165
But why isn't she coming out?

511
00:33:13,873 --> 00:33:16,290
Na-hee! Shin PD is here.

512
00:33:16,373 --> 00:33:18,998
What? Na-hee is here too?

513
00:33:19,081 --> 00:33:21,457
Did she just mean for me to eat and leave?

514
00:33:21,539 --> 00:33:23,498
Was I getting the wrong idea?

515
00:33:23,581 --> 00:33:26,123
- But there's no meeting today...
- It was...

516
00:33:27,623 --> 00:33:28,623
a joke.

517
00:33:33,623 --> 00:33:34,789
I'm alone.

518
00:33:35,332 --> 00:33:37,123
One serving isn't enough, even for me.

519
00:33:41,748 --> 00:33:43,831
Get a grip.

520
00:33:45,081 --> 00:33:47,831
I was just joking because
you seemed so nervous.

521
00:33:51,207 --> 00:33:52,373
Please sit down.
Make yourself comfortable.

522
00:34:04,248 --> 00:34:05,915
It's a good thing we have eggs, at least.

523
00:34:17,373 --> 00:34:18,581
By the way...

524
00:34:21,873 --> 00:34:22,956
Are we only having

525
00:34:23,956 --> 00:34:24,956
cold noodles?

526
00:34:26,081 --> 00:34:27,081
Sorry?

527
00:34:27,165 --> 00:34:28,831
I was wondering if this is all...

528
00:34:30,456 --> 00:34:32,165
It won't be enough, will it?

529
00:34:32,415 --> 00:34:34,290
Grilled meat with it would be nice

530
00:34:34,373 --> 00:34:35,373
but we don't have any.

531
00:34:36,498 --> 00:34:38,664
- Should we just go out to eat?
- No.

532
00:34:39,873 --> 00:34:40,915
That's not it...

533
00:34:45,414 --> 00:34:46,414
I didn't get...

534
00:34:47,165 --> 00:34:48,165
an answer.

535
00:34:51,207 --> 00:34:52,248
Because you didn't...

536
00:34:53,040 --> 00:34:54,414
answer me, Ms. Kim.

537
00:34:56,332 --> 00:34:57,373
Right.

538
00:35:02,248 --> 00:35:03,290
So?

539
00:35:08,956 --> 00:35:10,456
I asked you

540
00:35:10,831 --> 00:35:12,915
to have lunch with me.

541
00:35:15,165 --> 00:35:17,956
That's why I'm boiling water now.

542
00:35:21,498 --> 00:35:22,498
Is that...

543
00:35:22,873 --> 00:35:24,040
your answer?

544
00:35:45,248 --> 00:35:46,372
Is this the place?

545
00:36:10,915 --> 00:36:11,915
Hi.

546
00:36:11,998 --> 00:36:14,248
I'm Soon-rok's Love Cell.

547
00:36:14,456 --> 00:36:16,248
I came because I have something to say.

548
00:36:19,165 --> 00:36:20,290
I've been waiting.

549
00:36:22,414 --> 00:36:24,081
Thank you for coming back.

550
00:36:24,165 --> 00:36:26,456
I thought I'd never get another chance.

551
00:36:29,956 --> 00:36:30,998
Welcome.

552
00:36:32,748 --> 00:36:33,915
It's nice to meet you.

553
00:36:45,165 --> 00:36:46,207
I...

554
00:36:47,789 --> 00:36:50,414
like you too, Shin PD.

555
00:36:53,831 --> 00:36:55,248
Starting now

556
00:36:55,956 --> 00:36:57,289
let's give this a shot.

557
00:37:06,873 --> 00:37:07,873
Are you satisfied?

558
00:37:16,248 --> 00:37:17,289
Yes.

559
00:37:20,706 --> 00:37:21,748
Okay.

560
00:38:14,539 --> 00:38:15,956
Can I help you with anything?

561
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:17,414
Oh, no. Just stay seated.

562
00:38:17,498 --> 00:38:18,956
Or get yourself a drink.

563
00:38:19,040 --> 00:38:20,165
There are plenty in the fridge.

564
00:38:25,956 --> 00:38:26,998
Do you like bibim-naengmyeon?

565
00:38:30,081 --> 00:38:32,206
Yes, I prefer spicy
over non-spicy naengmyeon.

566
00:38:32,289 --> 00:38:33,664
How about you, Shin PD?

567
